Package au.edu.federation.caliko.visualisation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Axis
    A class to represent a 3D axis which consists of three drawn lines, one each in the +x, +y and +z directions.
    Camera
    Class to represent a 3D camera.
    Circle3D
    Class to draw a circle in 3D space.
    Entity
    A wrapper class which takes a Model and a ShaderProgram, then performs Vertex Array Object setup in order to allow easy drawing of the Model via the ShaderProgram.
    FabrikConstraint3D
    A class to draw various constraints for ball and hinge joints on FabrikBone3D objects.
    FabrikLine2D
    A static class used to draw a 2D lines to represent FabrikBone2D, FabrikChain2D or FabrickStructure2D objects.
    FabrikLine3D
    A static class used to draw a 3D lines to represent FabrikBone3D, FabrikChain3D or FabrikStructure3D objects.
    FabrikModel3D
    A class to represent a 3D model that can easily be attached to a FabrikBone3D object.
    Grid  
    Line2D
    Class to draw a line in 2D space.
    Line3D
    Class to draw a lines as well as circles and cones made from lines in 3D space.
    Model
    A class to represent and load a 3D model in WaveFront .OBJ format.
    MovingTarget3D
    Class to move a target around in 3D.
    Point2D
    Class to draw a point in 2D space.
    Point3D
    Class to draw a point in 3D space.
    ShaderProgram
    A class to represent an OpenGL shader program.
